user_instruction: 'Compose an email to Emily (emily@communityunited.org), the head of non-profit to discuss how we can boost our donation effort. You can check out my Gmail and Notion for information.'

formatted_items.arguments:
{"to":["emily@communityunited.org"],"subject":"Exploring New Ways to Boost Our Joint Donation Efforts","body":"Hi Emily,

I hope you're doing well! As we look ahead to the next quarter, I'd love to explore ways our two organizations can work together to amplify donations and deepen community engagement.

A few initial ideas I've been jotting down:

• Launch a “Steps for Change” virtual marathon where participants log miles throughout a week and secure peer-to-peer pledges.
• Host an online benefit concert featuring local artists; we could stream it on social platforms and encourage micro-donations throughout the show.
• Curate a community art auction showcasing pieces from neighborhood artists, with proceeds split between our missions.
• Leverage corporate matching-gift programs; we can jointly create a simple toolkit that employers can share internally.

If these resonate, perhaps we could schedule a 30-minute brainstorming call early next week to map out next steps and responsibilities. I’m flexible Monday or Tuesday between 10 am-1 pm ET, but happy to adjust.

Let me know what works for you, and feel free to toss in any other concepts you have on your radar.

Looking forward to collaborating!

Warmly,
John
Hope and Growth Foundation","cc":null,"bcc":null,"execution_log_path":"data/logs/item88_execution_log.json"}
